data.description: Nestled in Altoona, this ranch-style gem seamlessly blends comfort with sophistication. A 3-car garage beckons, leading to a practical mudroom/laundry space for seamless entries. Inside, the open floor plan boasts vaulted ceilings, creating an expansive living area anchored by a warm fireplace. The dining area elegantly links the chef's dream kitchen to the inviting living room. Three bedrooms, including a master with vaulted ceilings, ensuite, and walk-in closet, offer a haven of luxury. A second bathroom ensures convenience. The unfinished basement holds vast potential. Outside, a fenced yard and a composite deck with a pergola create a private retreat, perfect for relaxation or entertaining. All information obtained from Seller and pulbic records.
